WEBVTT

00:06.000 --> 00:12.074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

01:47.833 --> 01:48.959
I die

01:49.125 --> 01:50.547
for the Revolution.

01:51.958 --> 01:54.837
No Chinese Woman has yet shed blood
for the Revolution.

01:55.375 --> 01:57.002
I shall be the first,

01:57.500 --> 02:00.344
although the world doesn't know much
about the Revolution.

02:00.833 --> 02:03.211
I leave behind my husband and children.

02:05.833 --> 02:07.301
My death

02:07.875 --> 02:10.502
is my contribution to the Revolution.

02:12.625 --> 02:16.505
It will build an indestructible home
for all people,

02:17.500 --> 02:20.709
a peaceful and calm world for all children.

02:22.833 --> 02:26.713
The long-enslaved masses are numb,

02:28.083 --> 02:31.587
they know not peace, nor calm.

02:41.042 --> 02:42.134
These two children

02:42.625 --> 02:43.421
will soon lose their mother.

02:43.583 --> 02:45.711
I die for all children.

03:00.917 --> 03:03.511
I die for the Revolution.

03:04.458 --> 03:08.133
I'm not afraid, nor do I care about death.

03:08.875 --> 03:12.925
I rejoice at my martyrdom:

03:14.125 --> 03:16.594
At this moment

03:17.208 --> 03:18.926
I cry with blissful tears.

04:18.666 --> 04:20.464
Put the donation boxes in prominent spots.

04:20.625 --> 04:21.672
Go over to the door.

04:21.833 --> 04:22.834
Be vigilant.

04:23.000 --> 04:23.796
Yes.

04:26.333 --> 04:27.630
Let Mr. Sun rest.

04:27.792 --> 04:28.384
Don't disturb him.

04:28.542 --> 04:29.293
Yes.

05:17.042 --> 05:18.385
Juemin.

05:18.792 --> 05:19.384
Who's that?

05:19.792 --> 05:20.258
Who?

05:20.417 --> 05:21.213
Look.

05:22.958 --> 05:24.551
What?

05:30.542 --> 05:34.126
Go, quick.

05:34.708 --> 05:36.085
Get up, there's a woman here.

05:36.250 --> 05:37.251
Don't bother, just go.

06:04.625 --> 06:05.296
Keqiang.

06:05.667 --> 06:06.338
Time to get up.

06:06.500 --> 06:07.092
Get up.

06:07.542 --> 06:09.010
Let me sleep three more minutes.

06:09.250 --> 06:10.126
Alright.

06:10.292 --> 06:11.339
Get up.

06:12.375 --> 06:13.046
Two minutes.

06:14.292 --> 06:15.088
Fine.

06:16.958 --> 06:18.175
Two minutes.

06:39.292 --> 06:40.418
One minutes.

07:02.792 --> 07:04.009
I'll get up.

07:05.125 --> 07:06.593
I should go to Guangzhou for the uprising.

07:06.750 --> 07:07.717
What?

07:08.958 --> 07:10.960
You forgot the committee's
decision last night?

07:11.208 --> 07:12.585
Keqiang, listen.

07:12.750 --> 07:13.467
I won't.

07:13.750 --> 07:15.752
I must throw myself into battle.

07:16.000 --> 07:17.547
Then last night's meeting was a waste.

07:17.792 --> 07:19.260
Why can't we talk it through again?

07:19.417 --> 07:20.669
There's nothing to discuss.

07:22.042 --> 07:23.669
Huang Xing leads the Guangzhou uprising.

07:23.917 --> 07:25.760
Sun Wen handles fundraising overseas.

07:26.042 --> 07:27.385
We voted.

07:27.833 --> 07:28.629
Promise.

07:29.167 --> 07:30.134
Promise.

07:32.958 --> 07:34.631
These are donations from abroad.

07:36.167 --> 07:37.589
Overseas Chinese helped us.

07:38.417 --> 07:40.840
I promised them.

07:41.667 --> 07:43.044
I cannot fail them,

07:43.375 --> 07:45.093
I must carry out my pledge.

07:45.583 --> 07:47.051
It's not a personal promise

07:47.208 --> 07:48.960
but Tongmenghui's promise.

07:51.500 --> 07:52.672
They wrote these letters.

07:58.333 --> 07:59.334
Who's this Woman?

07:59.958 --> 08:01.335
Zonghan.

08:02.167 --> 08:03.009
Xu Zonghan.

08:03.458 --> 08:05.131
Tongmenghui member from my village.

08:06.042 --> 08:06.884
I'm Huang Xing.

08:09.125 --> 08:11.548
Zonghan coordinates underground
organizations in Guangzhou.

08:11.875 --> 08:13.627
You two pretend to be husband and wife.

08:13.833 --> 08:15.176
It's a good cover.

08:16.833 --> 08:18.460
No, it's not appropriate.

08:18.625 --> 08:19.922
Why not?

08:20.333 --> 08:21.676
I'm a woman and I don't care.

08:21.833 --> 08:22.880
What are you afraid of?

08:24.875 --> 08:26.127
It's easy to die in battle,

08:26.417 --> 08:27.589
but hard to motivate the living.

08:27.750 --> 08:29.252
You have the difficult task.

08:31.708 --> 08:37.090
The Guangzhou uprising
will finish off the Qing Dynasty.

08:39.082 --> 08:40.380
Take this pocket watch.

08:42.082 --> 08:43.083
On the day of the uprising,

08:43.582 --> 08:45.176
we'll monitor time together.

09:05.417 --> 09:05.918
Go,

09:06.083 --> 09:06.754
Charge.

09:27.833 --> 09:28.629
Quick.

09:41.750 --> 09:43.172
Quick.

10:02.917 --> 10:04.965
Destroy this wall.

10:05.250 --> 10:06.046
Yes.

10:10.542 --> 10:11.839
You rebel.

10:13.042 --> 10:14.294
You dare revolt.

10:20.208 --> 10:21.585
You revolutionary.

10:28.333 --> 10:29.459
You dare revolt.

10:31.833 --> 10:32.925
You...

10:33.333 --> 10:34.255
You...

10:43.750 --> 10:44.672
Where's Zhang Mingqi?

10:44.917 --> 10:45.543
I don't know.

10:50.250 --> 10:51.217
Quick.

10:51.625 --> 10:52.717
And my Wife.

10:53.333 --> 10:54.380
Quick.

11:03.250 --> 11:05.924
Comrades taking part in the uprising

11:06.083 --> 11:07.335
know me better.

11:07.500 --> 11:08.296
It's easier for me to coordinate...

11:08.458 --> 11:09.630
Nonsense.

11:10.292 --> 11:11.544
I can wield my pen

11:11.708 --> 11:12.504
and scalpel,

11:12.667 --> 11:13.919
why not a gun?

11:14.083 --> 11:16.381
Remember: You're still a wanted man
by the Qing court,

11:16.625 --> 11:17.797
you can't risk it.

11:17.958 --> 11:19.756
If you return to China
to lead the uprising,

11:20.208 --> 11:21.755
you're being irresponsible.

11:31.208 --> 11:31.925
Yu Peilun.

11:32.417 --> 11:33.293
Yu Peilun.

11:34.083 --> 11:35.005
Yu Peilun.

11:35.417 --> 11:36.134
Here.

11:37.958 --> 11:39.505
We couldn't Contact the other groups.

11:40.042 --> 11:41.043
Zhang Mingqi ran away.

11:41.208 --> 11:42.425
Keqiang said,

11:42.750 --> 11:43.922
if the uprising fails,

11:44.458 --> 11:45.550
you must inform Sun Wen immediately.

11:45.708 --> 11:46.425
What else did he say?

11:46.792 --> 11:47.668
He said,

11:48.375 --> 11:49.467
if he's not back by dusk,

11:49.917 --> 11:51.339
you must leave Guangzhou at once.

11:52.792 --> 11:53.543
Quick.

12:12.125 --> 12:14.127
Back off. All of you.

12:14.667 --> 12:16.135
Listen to my command.

12:16.292 --> 12:17.293
Attack from the sides.

12:17.458 --> 12:18.380
- Yes.
- Hand grenades.

12:18.833 --> 12:19.925
- Yes.
- Follow me.

12:25.917 --> 12:27.635
Charge.

12:31.292 --> 12:32.214
Keqiang.

12:35.792 --> 12:36.509
Your hand.

12:36.750 --> 12:37.125
Keqiang.

12:37.333 --> 12:38.835
Don't mind me, charge.

12:39.000 --> 12:39.671
Yes.

12:39.833 --> 12:40.675
Charge.

13:26.333 --> 13:28.051
Get away.

13:49.625 --> 13:50.547
Run.

13:50.708 --> 13:51.709
- What are you doing?
- Run.

13:58.500 --> 13:59.717
Let me go.

14:00.083 --> 14:01.175
Let me go.

14:12.250 --> 14:13.752
Yu Peilun.

14:44.958 --> 14:45.925
Gentlemen,

14:46.583 --> 14:47.835
our fundraiser today

14:48.250 --> 14:50.628
was originally organized
for the Guangzhou uprising.

14:52.292 --> 14:53.714
But just now,

14:54.500 --> 14:55.797
I received news.

14:57.208 --> 14:59.085
Fighting in Guangzhou has ceased.

15:00.667 --> 15:02.965
The uprising has failed.

15:08.625 --> 15:09.592
The telegram states,

15:10.125 --> 15:11.502
the uprising failed,

15:12.750 --> 15:15.173
many of our core members are dead.

15:15.625 --> 15:17.252
You've never met them.

15:19.542 --> 15:24.127
These young people who died were talented,

15:24.750 --> 15:26.343
some came from rich families,

15:27.167 --> 15:28.919
some have just gotten married.

15:29.375 --> 15:31.719
They were willing to sacrifice themselves,

15:32.000 --> 15:33.627
whatever the cost.

15:34.667 --> 15:36.294
They sacrificed their lives for the cause

15:38.542 --> 15:40.044
because they have faith.

15:40.208 --> 15:41.084
What do your lies

15:41.250 --> 15:42.547
have to do with us?

15:42.917 --> 15:43.884
Good question.

15:44.667 --> 15:45.668
Most of you gathered here

15:46.167 --> 15:47.794
are overseas Chinese.

15:48.167 --> 15:49.510
You know Well

15:50.042 --> 15:52.420
our faces mark us as Chinese,

15:53.042 --> 15:55.170
and we've suffered discrimination

15:55.375 --> 15:56.297
and bullying.

15:56.500 --> 15:58.173
We've endured unfair treatment.

15:58.583 --> 16:01.177
All because the country of our people

16:01.667 --> 16:03.089
has long been corrupt

16:03.417 --> 16:04.464
and weak,

16:04.833 --> 16:06.255
writhing in pain.

16:07.042 --> 16:09.841
Our Chinese compatriots

16:10.208 --> 16:11.209
face adversity,

16:11.500 --> 16:12.626
our land taken by others.

16:13.750 --> 16:15.172
Our Revolution

16:15.667 --> 16:17.840
ensures people can pursue happiness,

16:18.167 --> 16:20.044
that our race will regain dignity.

16:21.083 --> 16:24.257
The Chinese revolutionary movement is
blessed by support from overseas Chinese.

16:24.958 --> 16:25.800
For many years,

16:26.208 --> 16:27.710
I strongly believe this.

16:28.208 --> 16:31.052
Overseas Chinese are the
mother of the Revolution.

16:32.708 --> 16:33.675
Gentlemen,

16:36.042 --> 16:37.464
your children

16:42.917 --> 16:44.419
have died for you.

16:45.167 --> 16:46.214
Fang Shengdong.

16:49.292 --> 16:50.464
Lin Shishuang.

16:54.417 --> 16:55.464
Yu Peilun.

16:58.375 --> 16:59.467
Chen Gengxin.

17:03.333 --> 17:04.334
Lin Juemin.

17:06.916 --> 17:09.011
This young man will soon be a father.

17:33.458 --> 17:33.959
What's this?

17:34.208 --> 17:35.505
US $300,000.00

17:36.000 --> 17:37.468
Donation from Zhigongtang

17:39.458 --> 17:40.675
I won't hide this from you.

17:41.167 --> 17:43.795
We sold our ancestral house.

17:48.958 --> 17:49.880
Yat-sen,

17:50.625 --> 17:53.219
we're overseas Chinese,

17:53.958 --> 17:55.960
our roots are in China.

17:56.500 --> 17:58.173
The Qing Dynasty is no longer our home.

17:58.875 --> 18:00.172
Without a place called home,

18:01.792 --> 18:03.214
why Keep an ancestral house?

18:12.542 --> 18:13.418
Take it.

18:14.792 --> 18:16.339
If the Revolution fails,

18:17.875 --> 18:19.718
you'll owe us for generations.

18:41.417 --> 18:42.339
Another one.

19:12.833 --> 19:13.800
Yat-sen,

19:15.000 --> 19:16.092
your pocket Watch

19:16.542 --> 19:17.634
can block bullets,

19:19.542 --> 19:21.044
but not cannon shells.

19:26.083 --> 19:26.754
Fire.

19:54.917 --> 19:56.089
Empress Dowager,

19:56.375 --> 19:57.092
I hear.

19:57.250 --> 19:58.797
Sun Wen has long escaped abroad,

19:58.917 --> 20:00.544
he hasn't returned for more than a decade.

20:00.708 --> 20:01.834
We might want to arrest him,

20:02.083 --> 20:03.835
but it's going to be hard.

20:04.542 --> 20:06.920
Didn't we alert our envoys

20:07.083 --> 20:08.676
and foreign governments

20:08.917 --> 20:10.794
about Sun, telling them

20:10.917 --> 20:12.715
they should monitor his movements?

20:13.042 --> 20:15.511
But Sun gives public lectures everywhere,

20:16.250 --> 20:18.002
raising funds, organizing rebels,

20:18.167 --> 20:19.794
trafficking arms, plotting uprisings.

20:19.958 --> 20:21.676
Minister Xu, perhaps you overstate.

20:22.292 --> 20:24.590
He hasn't appeared before our eyes.

20:24.958 --> 20:26.380
He's only mortal,

20:26.625 --> 20:27.877
not the Monkey King.

20:28.292 --> 20:29.965
What power can he wield?

20:31.625 --> 20:33.878
Sun's done enough to rock the boat.

20:34.250 --> 20:36.799
These years, unrest seethes everywhere,

20:36.958 --> 20:38.835
rebellions follow one after another.

20:39.250 --> 20:41.503
Sun's been misleading others with his lies,

20:41.708 --> 20:44.177
so many follow his path.

20:45.292 --> 20:46.965
What a troublemaker.

20:47.292 --> 20:49.670
As if he doesn't make enough trouble.

20:49.958 --> 20:52.086
The Qing Dynasty will not
fall because of him.

20:52.625 --> 20:53.877
If he dares enter the Forbidden City,

20:54.083 --> 20:55.585
our Manchurian imperial army will kill him.

20:55.875 --> 20:56.467
Yes,

20:56.750 --> 20:57.626
let's just eradicate.

20:58.000 --> 20:59.502
Sun Wen and his cohorts.

20:59.750 --> 21:01.673
We'll destroy them once and for all.

21:01.958 --> 21:03.255
Stop carrying on like this.

21:04.667 --> 21:06.465
No matter whether to kill them,

21:06.625 --> 21:07.842
or praise or punish them,

21:08.708 --> 21:10.881
or whatever other solution,

21:11.083 --> 21:13.085
I only have this to say:

21:13.875 --> 21:15.218
Please, all of you,

21:15.583 --> 21:18.587
let Us have some peace.

21:25.417 --> 21:26.293
Recently,

21:26.667 --> 21:28.510
the mortgage of our railways

21:28.667 --> 21:31.011
against the Four Nations Bank loan

21:31.375 --> 21:32.672
has led to riots.

21:33.333 --> 21:35.506
What's the use of your rifles?

21:36.000 --> 21:37.297
Tell them:

21:37.583 --> 21:38.960
If they revolt,

21:39.875 --> 21:41.377
they'll all die in vain.

21:54.417 --> 21:55.669
Lin Juemin.

21:56.917 --> 21:58.510
You're educated,

21:58.958 --> 22:00.460
you come from a good family.

22:01.625 --> 22:05.334
Why did you join the rebels?

22:08.917 --> 22:09.793
Zhang Mingqi,

22:11.000 --> 22:12.468
why do you hide in darkness?

22:14.375 --> 22:15.547
What are you afraid of?

22:17.417 --> 22:18.418
What am I afraid of?

22:18.708 --> 22:19.800
You're afraid of my youth.

22:20.500 --> 22:21.467
I have chosen death,

22:21.917 --> 22:23.294
but I'm still young.

22:24.958 --> 22:26.130
You might live,

22:26.958 --> 22:28.505
but you are old and worthless.

22:34.667 --> 22:36.089
Have you read the study of evolution?

22:36.792 --> 22:38.089
Survival of the fittest.

22:39.500 --> 22:40.547
Have you considered

22:41.583 --> 22:42.425
the leading nations in the world

22:42.583 --> 22:45.427
were all borne of revolution?

22:46.583 --> 22:47.926
China must also have a revolution.

22:48.083 --> 22:49.050
Affairs of the nation

22:49.917 --> 22:50.634
are not your concern.

22:50.792 --> 22:52.044
Sun Wen said,

22:53.417 --> 22:54.418
China is Weak.

22:55.458 --> 22:57.210
There's no way out.

22:57.417 --> 22:58.669
The royal family, aristocrats and officials

22:58.833 --> 23:00.335
all follow their old ways,

23:00.500 --> 23:01.501
but what of the people?

23:01.708 --> 23:03.381
They barely survive, ignorant of the world.

23:03.542 --> 23:04.634
China is no match for other countries,

23:05.083 --> 23:06.960
it's a dire situation.

23:07.458 --> 23:08.254
Young man,

23:08.667 --> 23:10.544
the Qing court has a hard time too.

23:12.042 --> 23:13.089
The court?

23:13.667 --> 23:15.886
The court gave Hong Kong to England

23:16.292 --> 23:17.714
and Taiwan to Japan.

23:17.958 --> 23:19.084
That's the good Work of the Qing court.

23:19.250 --> 23:20.797
What's the use of keeping it?

23:24.583 --> 23:25.584
I'm interrogating you,

23:25.792 --> 23:27.294
yet you turn around to question me?

23:27.458 --> 23:29.256
You have no grounds to sentence me.

23:34.500 --> 23:35.296
Lin Juemin,

23:35.583 --> 23:37.301
I had wanted to exercise clemency.

23:37.458 --> 23:38.129
There's no need.

23:38.625 --> 23:39.751
My comrades and I fought together,

23:40.958 --> 23:42.050
we'll die together.

23:43.042 --> 23:44.259
I can't be an exception.

23:45.292 --> 23:46.669
When you die,

23:47.500 --> 23:49.468
you'll be left with nothing.

23:49.917 --> 23:51.294
The Qing court wants my life;

23:53.250 --> 23:54.502
I'll destroy the dynasty at its heart.

25:28.875 --> 25:29.876
Hello, Your Royal Highness,

25:30.250 --> 25:32.628
this is a car used by British royalty.

25:33.875 --> 25:37.254
As a member of Chinese royalty, let me try.

25:38.500 --> 25:39.296
Please.

25:40.000 --> 25:42.594
You've come because of
the Sichuan railways?

25:43.417 --> 25:45.761
The loan agreements between our countries

25:46.000 --> 25:49.254
and the mortgage of your railways
cannot be written off.

25:49.417 --> 25:50.839
That's the trouble.

25:51.167 --> 25:52.464
I knew it.

25:52.625 --> 25:55.253
The mortgage of the Sichuan
and Guangdong railways

25:55.458 --> 25:56.630
against your loan

25:56.917 --> 25:58.339
will lead to trouble down the road.

25:58.750 --> 26:00.093
If you forcibly take the railways,

26:00.333 --> 26:01.801
it'll be a catastrophe.

26:02.875 --> 26:06.175
Can't we find a solution, my dear lord?

26:07.458 --> 26:09.085
Look at this invention.

26:09.417 --> 26:10.919
It's an iron machine.

26:11.125 --> 26:13.628
It can move forward and backward,

26:14.292 --> 26:15.965
left and right,

26:16.500 --> 26:17.501
whatever you wish.

26:17.667 --> 26:18.293
My lord,

26:18.500 --> 26:19.717
please enjoy this humble gift

26:19.958 --> 26:22.461
and steer it in the right direction.

26:22.792 --> 26:23.884
Mr. Ambassador,

26:24.750 --> 26:26.002
we've already sent troops from Wuchang

26:26.208 --> 26:29.132
to suppress the Sichuan riots.

26:29.875 --> 26:31.001
Don't you worry.

26:31.167 --> 26:33.090
Your Royal Highness,
you're a great strategist.

26:34.167 --> 26:36.636
You're the one holding the steering wheel.

26:37.375 --> 26:38.843
You have money,

26:39.125 --> 26:40.672
you have navel fleets,

26:41.125 --> 26:44.299
you've always been better
businessmen than us.

26:48.167 --> 26:49.510
In 50 years,

26:50.000 --> 26:51.877
the car you gave me

26:52.125 --> 26:53.968
will be scrap metal,

26:54.250 --> 26:56.503
but my little gift to you

26:56.667 --> 26:58.635
will be priceless.

27:01.542 --> 27:02.213
Thank you.

27:07.250 --> 27:08.126
Open the door. Huang Keqiang.

27:08.500 --> 27:09.752
Quick, open the door. Huang Keqiang

27:10.125 --> 27:11.126
I Know you're inside..

27:12.125 --> 27:12.921
Open,

27:13.167 --> 27:14.009
Huang Keqiang.

27:21.083 --> 27:21.754
Huang Keqiang,

27:22.250 --> 27:23.001
open the door.

27:29.083 --> 27:30.426
Open the door for me.

27:35.042 --> 27:37.261
What are you doing?

27:37.542 --> 27:38.714
Put it down.

27:39.083 --> 27:40.835
Give me the blade.

27:41.000 --> 27:41.546
Let me go.

27:41.708 --> 27:43.255
What are you doing?

27:43.750 --> 27:46.299
What?

27:48.125 --> 27:49.672
You can't die.

27:54.292 --> 27:56.215
I know you saw

27:56.458 --> 27:59.177
all of them being killed.

28:00.167 --> 28:01.009
I know

28:02.833 --> 28:04.301
we failed.

28:04.417 --> 28:06.090
I didn't want to die, Zonghan

28:08.042 --> 28:09.419
I want to keep this hand

28:09.792 --> 28:10.759
to wield the gun.

28:14.583 --> 28:15.584
Help me,

28:16.292 --> 28:17.589
chop it off.

28:18.417 --> 28:19.168
No.

28:19.542 --> 28:20.589
- No.
- So we failed,

28:20.750 --> 28:21.876
we've failed before.

28:22.042 --> 28:22.588
No.

28:41.792 --> 28:42.543
Children,

28:42.792 --> 28:44.635
do you know what the telegram says?

28:44.792 --> 28:45.964
No.

28:46.125 --> 28:47.377
Huang Keqiang is alive.

28:47.750 --> 28:49.002
Fate has been kind.

28:49.167 --> 28:50.589
Who's he?

28:51.792 --> 28:52.793
Huang Keqiang

28:53.292 --> 28:55.044
is a strong and determined man,

28:55.333 --> 28:56.835
a man who won't die.

28:57.000 --> 28:58.923
We don't know him.

28:59.125 --> 29:01.048
But do you know Homer Lea?

29:01.333 --> 29:02.334
Yes.

29:02.500 --> 29:03.467
Take me to him, please.

29:03.875 --> 29:04.626
Yes.

29:06.042 --> 29:06.918
Where's Homer Lea?

29:07.083 --> 29:09.302
There.

29:09.458 --> 29:10.425
Homer Lea.

29:10.583 --> 29:11.835
Homer.

29:15.625 --> 29:16.751
Homer.

29:18.958 --> 29:21.677
- Homer.
- Hey, I'm here.

29:28.667 --> 29:29.338
Mr. Lea,

29:29.625 --> 29:30.171
tell me.

29:30.500 --> 29:32.878
Why are you so interested
in Chinese revolution?

29:33.208 --> 29:34.380
Nowadays,

29:34.667 --> 29:35.668
a Chinese revolution

29:35.833 --> 29:38.052
is the only thing that can
make exciting history.

29:41.333 --> 29:42.380
Exciting?

29:43.042 --> 29:46.546
That's not what our revolution is about.

29:47.500 --> 29:48.672
Why revolution?

29:51.083 --> 29:52.460
I was once a doctor.

29:53.333 --> 29:55.006
I used to save a lot of lives

29:55.500 --> 29:56.592
with my scalpel.

29:58.167 --> 29:59.089
But sadly,

29:59.375 --> 30:00.422
in my country,

30:00.708 --> 30:02.881
life is so miserable

30:03.833 --> 30:05.961
it might be Worse than death.

30:07.417 --> 30:08.634
I always wonder

30:08.875 --> 30:09.967
why my compatriots

30:10.125 --> 30:12.719
have to endure their lives with no dignity.

30:13.042 --> 30:14.885
They survive like animals

30:15.708 --> 30:17.335
with very basic needs,

30:17.708 --> 30:20.962
suffering the oppression
from the ruling class

30:21.333 --> 30:22.835
and foreign powers.

30:24.000 --> 30:24.717
Now,

30:25.542 --> 30:26.714
I cannot accept it,

30:26.958 --> 30:28.460
I will not accept it.

30:28.875 --> 30:30.218
I want to change.

30:30.625 --> 30:32.002
I want a revolution.

30:35.667 --> 30:36.338
Come,

30:37.125 --> 30:38.092
I'll show you.

30:40.583 --> 30:43.006
Recently, in Sichuan,

30:43.417 --> 30:47.092
the central part of China,
people have launched a movement

30:47.250 --> 30:51.926
of protecting railway projects against
the hopelessly corrupt Qing government.

30:52.375 --> 30:59.008
It is said that the Qing government has to
mobilize the army from Hubei province o Sichuan.

31:00.458 --> 31:05.134
What they don't know is many officers
who stayed behind in the army of.

31:05.292 --> 31:08.717
Hubei, Hunan, and Jiangsu,

31:09.250 --> 31:13.130
are active members of Tongmenghui,
the Restoration League,

31:13.750 --> 31:14.751
I have a feeling

31:15.292 --> 31:17.169
that in the south of Yangtze River,

31:18.042 --> 31:19.760
an even bigger movement

31:20.083 --> 31:21.209
will take hold.

31:21.458 --> 31:23.051
I want to join your revolution.

31:24.083 --> 31:25.005
That's fine.

31:25.458 --> 31:26.835
I would like to invite you

31:27.000 --> 31:30.504
to join the Chinese Revolution
as a military advisor,

31:30.958 --> 31:34.792
but I'm afraid I cannot afford you
and pay the attention that you deserve.

31:34.958 --> 31:35.629
This,

31:36.000 --> 31:37.422
this is not about money.

31:37.583 --> 31:38.880
It's about you, Sun.

31:39.208 --> 31:43.258
You must be China's revolutionary leader.

31:48.792 --> 31:49.759
I promise you.

32:02.792 --> 32:03.918
Peng Chufan.

32:04.458 --> 32:06.802
Liu Fuji. Yang Hongsheng.

32:07.750 --> 32:09.127
The three of them plotted mutiny.

32:10.000 --> 32:11.297
Today punishment is upon them.

32:12.083 --> 32:14.131
We execute them today

32:14.667 --> 32:15.884
as a Warning to all.

32:17.000 --> 32:17.842
Among you...

32:18.000 --> 32:18.592
Governor,

32:18.792 --> 32:20.669
we found the list. What should we do?

32:21.125 --> 32:22.843
What else can we do with

32:23.625 --> 32:24.626
those rebels from the Gongjinhui?

32:25.292 --> 32:26.464
Starting tonight,

32:27.083 --> 32:28.130
kill everyone on the list.

32:28.292 --> 32:29.635
No one will be spared.

32:38.167 --> 32:38.713
All of you,

32:39.667 --> 32:41.385
ask your own conscience.

32:42.500 --> 32:44.002
The Qing court supports

32:44.167 --> 32:45.339
and protects you,

32:45.833 --> 32:46.629
yet you plot to rebel,

32:47.333 --> 32:49.711
following such thugs as Sun Wen.

32:50.333 --> 32:52.176
Isn't that the behavior of unfilial sons,

32:52.708 --> 32:54.676
killing their parents?

33:04.167 --> 33:05.293
Stop, you two.

33:07.333 --> 33:09.677
What are your names?

33:09.833 --> 33:11.130
Xiong Bingkun of the 8th regiment,
8th engineering battalion.

33:11.292 --> 33:12.714
Jin Zheolong of the 8th regiment,
8th engineering battalion.

33:12.875 --> 33:13.592
Lie low.

33:13.750 --> 33:14.672
This is a crisis.

33:14.833 --> 33:15.584
Don't be hot-tempered.

33:15.750 --> 33:16.501
Yes.

33:19.875 --> 33:20.717
What is this?

33:21.958 --> 33:22.880
A mutiny?

33:23.208 --> 33:24.084
Not sleeping?

33:26.292 --> 33:27.214
What do you want?

33:27.375 --> 33:28.297
What?

33:28.583 --> 33:29.209
This is a mutiny.

33:29.375 --> 33:30.217
Tao Qisheng.

33:36.833 --> 33:37.584
Brother,

33:39.083 --> 33:39.925
put down your rifle.

33:40.208 --> 33:41.425
I'm leading a mutiny.

33:42.708 --> 33:44.676
How many more will you kill?

33:45.375 --> 33:46.592
You're lucky that

33:47.083 --> 33:48.380
I'm aiming at you.

33:48.583 --> 33:49.084
Brother,

33:49.417 --> 33:50.885
this is not a joke.

33:51.250 --> 33:52.877
If we don't do it now, then when?

33:53.083 --> 33:53.959
Help.

34:15.625 --> 34:17.172
Tell Zhang Zhenwu to bring
two of his battalions.

34:17.333 --> 34:18.926
Aim all artillery at the
Governor's mansion.

34:19.083 --> 34:20.005
When Xiong Bingkun lights the torch,

34:20.167 --> 34:21.918
fire at the mansion.

34:22.083 --> 34:22.754
Yes.

34:24.083 --> 34:25.676
Charge.

34:34.917 --> 34:35.839
Hand grenades.

34:41.292 --> 34:42.168
Go.

34:55.625 --> 34:56.376
Jin Zhaolong

34:56.958 --> 34:58.460
Jin Zhaolong, Xiong Bingkun.

34:58.667 --> 35:00.169
Lead two platoons.

35:00.333 --> 35:01.630
Order everyone to bring gas canisters.

35:01.792 --> 35:02.839
Rush in to fuel the fire.

35:03.125 --> 35:04.047
Light the target.

35:04.250 --> 35:04.796
Yes.

35:06.375 --> 35:07.501
- Quick.
- Quick.

35:08.167 --> 35:08.918
Quick.

35:09.458 --> 35:11.335
Quick.

35:22.042 --> 35:23.168
Ready,

35:23.458 --> 35:25.005
aiming at the Governor's mansion.

35:25.500 --> 35:27.093
Load.

35:27.542 --> 35:29.010
Done.

35:29.250 --> 35:30.502
Fire.

35:35.958 --> 35:37.210
Load.

35:37.375 --> 35:38.342
Fire.

35:47.333 --> 35:48.380
Good morning, Mrs. Johnson.

35:48.542 --> 35:49.418
Good morning.

35:50.083 --> 35:50.629
Here.

35:50.833 --> 35:51.834
Oh, yes.

35:53.375 --> 35:54.501
Oh, Dr. Sun.

35:54.750 --> 35:55.251
Yes?

35:55.500 --> 35:58.583
It seems like there's something
in today's paper about China.

35:58.917 --> 35:59.634
Thank you.

36:28.250 --> 36:30.252
Do you need some help, Dr. Sun?

36:31.625 --> 36:33.252
Can I give you some water?

36:33.375 --> 36:35.252
I'm all right.

36:55.917 --> 36:56.588
Yat-sen.

36:56.958 --> 36:58.710
Hey, what's going on in here?

36:58.917 --> 37:00.009
What are you guys doing?

37:00.167 --> 37:01.669
Come on.

37:01.833 --> 37:04.427
Yat-sen. The Revolution has succeeded.

37:04.792 --> 37:06.294
- Hey, what's the matter with you?
- Sorry.

37:08.250 --> 37:09.422
On October 10,

37:09.625 --> 37:10.717
The Revolutionary army took over Wuchang.

37:10.875 --> 37:12.468
Governor Rui Cheng fled overnight.

37:12.750 --> 37:14.923
Wuchang revolutionaries telegraphed
the entire country,

37:15.083 --> 37:17.381
asking them to join in the rebellion.
The world's in shock.

37:17.583 --> 37:18.084
Yat-sen,

37:18.417 --> 37:19.339
you should return to China immediately.

37:19.500 --> 37:20.797
I'll reserve a boat ticket for you.

37:20.958 --> 37:23.302
You only need to spend 20 days across
the Pacific, then you'll reach Shanghai.

37:24.667 --> 37:25.714
It happened in Wuchang.

37:26.333 --> 37:27.585
It happened in Wuchang.

37:30.125 --> 37:31.627
Send a telegram to Keqiang in Hong Kong,

37:31.917 --> 37:33.794
so he travels to Wuchang
to lead the revolution.

37:33.958 --> 37:34.550
Yes.

37:37.458 --> 37:37.959
Sun,

37:38.375 --> 37:39.126
I'm ready.

37:39.542 --> 37:40.794
I'll go to China with you.

37:42.750 --> 37:43.626
No.

37:44.208 --> 37:45.710
I'm going to Europe first.

37:46.083 --> 37:48.336
Huang Xing is much better than me
to handle this in China.

37:48.500 --> 37:49.126
Why?

37:49.500 --> 37:50.501
The unrest in China

37:51.875 --> 37:56.005
will be closely linked to the
Four Nations Bank loan to the Qing court.

37:57.542 --> 37:59.590
The court's out of money now,

38:00.750 --> 38:02.127
but if they get the loan,

38:02.458 --> 38:03.710
they can thwart the revolution.

38:05.208 --> 38:06.505
Reserve tickets for Europe.

39:08.542 --> 39:08.963
Zonghan,

39:09.125 --> 39:10.001
don't bother making dinner.

39:10.333 --> 39:11.129
We're running out of time.

39:16.792 --> 39:17.714
Put it down.

39:17.875 --> 39:19.047
Why are you so anxious?

39:23.583 --> 39:24.926
You don't need it.

39:34.917 --> 39:36.919
The battle in Wuchang will be intense.

39:37.583 --> 39:39.085
I'm concerned for your safety.

39:39.250 --> 39:40.923
What about your own safety?

39:42.708 --> 39:43.504
Don't Worry,

39:43.792 --> 39:44.668
I won't die.

39:45.542 --> 39:46.964
Fate will be kind to me.

39:56.083 --> 39:57.130
I should go now.

40:01.250 --> 40:02.092
Go.

40:16.708 --> 40:17.630
What happened?

40:17.792 --> 40:19.794
Only yesterday Rui Cheng reported to us

40:20.042 --> 40:21.919
that the rebel leaders were killed.

40:22.083 --> 40:23.255
A day passed and...

40:23.417 --> 40:24.964
The New Army had it easy.

40:27.500 --> 40:28.296
Clearly,

40:28.542 --> 40:31.512
the Wuchang regiments were sent to Sichuan
to stop the unrest,

40:32.042 --> 40:34.136
so the city was unguarded...

40:34.292 --> 40:36.294
Tell me something I don't already know.

40:36.625 --> 40:38.969
The Qing court has ruled for more than 200 years.
We've ridden through many storms.

40:39.208 --> 40:41.210
It's only a small flame,
we'll extinguish it.

40:43.042 --> 40:43.964
Who should we send

40:44.500 --> 40:46.502
to extinguish this flame?

40:47.833 --> 40:48.504
Empress Dowager,

40:49.125 --> 40:50.217
I humbly believe...

40:53.167 --> 40:55.340
I recommend Yin Chang,
head of the Imperial Army.

40:55.625 --> 40:57.673
This is his duty.

40:59.792 --> 41:00.543
Xu Shichang.

41:00.667 --> 41:01.418
Yes.

41:02.458 --> 41:03.425
Just now,

41:04.000 --> 41:05.092
what were you saying?

41:05.333 --> 41:07.427
Yuan Shikai can fulfill this task.

41:10.667 --> 41:12.169
Better to appoint Yin Chang.

41:12.875 --> 41:14.127
This is family affair.

41:14.333 --> 41:15.835
It's better to send over a Manchu.

41:16.542 --> 41:17.168
Yes.

41:17.500 --> 41:18.217
Empress Dowager,

41:18.542 --> 41:20.169
I would like to submit a request.

41:25.542 --> 41:26.634
Say it, Royal Prince.

41:26.917 --> 41:29.170
Food and supplies precede an army.

41:29.417 --> 41:29.792
There's this old saying...

41:29.958 --> 41:31.756
Be precise,

41:31.917 --> 41:33.715
- don't just quote the classics.
- In my opinion,

41:34.208 --> 41:36.461
We should finalize the loan

41:36.667 --> 41:38.340
from the Four Nations Bank,

41:38.500 --> 41:40.093
we'll have less to worry about later.

41:40.458 --> 41:42.131
Haven't we discussed this for months?

41:42.667 --> 41:43.884
Why hasn't this been done?

41:44.208 --> 41:46.131
The Four Nations Bank felt

41:46.292 --> 41:49.045
we've been indecisive

41:49.292 --> 41:50.714
about mortgaging our railways.

41:51.042 --> 41:53.386
There's been criticism outside.

41:53.750 --> 41:54.751
People say that

41:54.958 --> 41:57.177
we're giving away our sovereignty.

41:58.708 --> 42:00.210
If we're not rulers here,

42:00.375 --> 42:01.592
is this even a country?

42:04.375 --> 42:04.841
General Li,

42:05.000 --> 42:06.968
for the sake of the times, please decide.

42:07.333 --> 42:09.051
I've treated you well.

42:09.417 --> 42:11.090
Why are you making it so difficult for me?

42:11.667 --> 42:12.964
We ask that you lead the
Military Government.

42:13.125 --> 42:14.502
We're not making it difficult.

42:15.042 --> 42:16.043
Drop your gun.

42:17.667 --> 42:18.714
Please ask him to drop his gun.

42:21.667 --> 42:22.543
Put it down.

42:29.542 --> 42:30.259
General Li,

42:31.208 --> 42:32.881
you've treated us well.

42:33.625 --> 42:36.094
We wish you'd lead the Military Government.

42:36.292 --> 42:37.919
You nave great talents
among the revolutionary ranks.

42:38.125 --> 42:39.342
Why don't you ask Sun
Wen to be your leader?

42:39.500 --> 42:40.342
Li Yuanhong.

42:40.917 --> 42:43.261
The revolutionary party
will select our leaders.

42:44.000 --> 42:44.717
At present.

42:44.875 --> 42:45.751
Sun Wen is still abroad,

42:46.208 --> 42:47.255
and Huang Keqiang is on his Way here.

42:47.500 --> 42:48.752
That's why we offer you this.

42:49.250 --> 42:49.796
Li Yuanhong,

42:50.083 --> 42:50.925
do you understand your predicament?

42:51.083 --> 42:52.505
I can give up my position
in the Qing court,

42:52.875 --> 42:54.798
but I don't want to become
a revolutionary official.

42:55.208 --> 42:56.084
I only want to return home.

42:58.208 --> 42:59.881
You have no idea of the real situation:

43:00.458 --> 43:02.256
Although Rui Cheng and Zhang Biao
have gone into hiding,

43:02.625 --> 43:04.502
if the court's troops
were to counterattack,

43:04.792 --> 43:07.671
they can destroy Wuchang in a second.

43:16.417 --> 43:16.792
Come back.

43:16.958 --> 43:17.800
Stop.

43:18.167 --> 43:19.464
- Come back.
- Go.

43:19.667 --> 43:20.293
Stop.

43:22.125 --> 43:22.967
Go.

43:33.708 --> 43:34.675
Lie down.

43:34.792 --> 43:36.465
Yin Chang's firing at us
from a German battleship.

43:36.667 --> 43:37.168
General Li,

43:37.333 --> 43:38.129
are you all right?

43:38.333 --> 43:39.676
What damned battle is this?

43:40.083 --> 43:41.926
I'll die because of you.

43:42.083 --> 43:43.505
Remove the ammunition, quick.

43:43.667 --> 43:44.839
We'll die together.

43:45.000 --> 43:46.593
We'll count you as a revolutionary martyr.

43:48.167 --> 43:50.340
Li Yuanhong, General of the Mixed Brigade.

43:50.875 --> 43:53.003
I'm Military Governor Li Yuanhong.

43:53.333 --> 43:54.300
If you Want to live,

43:54.458 --> 43:56.176
return to your stations.

43:59.500 --> 44:00.877
Attention.

44:01.042 --> 44:01.918
Yes.

