44:05.708 --> 44:09.508
Distance: 2400 feet.

44:09.750 --> 44:12.833
Load.

44:13.250 --> 44:14.843
Prepare for rapid firing, first round.

44:15.167 --> 44:17.841
Rapid firing, first round.

44:18.000 --> 44:19.718
Fire.

44:23.375 --> 44:24.297
Distance:

44:24.542 --> 44:26.169
2350 miles,

44:26.458 --> 44:27.755
25m to the right.

44:27.917 --> 44:29.043
Load.

44:29.208 --> 44:30.585
Fire all three cannons.

44:30.750 --> 44:31.967
Fire.

44:39.042 --> 44:40.419
Cease fire.

44:41.542 --> 44:42.589
Why did we stop?

44:43.167 --> 44:44.419
I'm the Military Governor,

44:44.750 --> 44:46.377
I make all the decisions.

44:46.667 --> 44:47.634
Why did they stop?

44:49.833 --> 44:50.755
They ran out of ammunition?

44:50.917 --> 44:51.543
Doesn't look like it.

44:52.208 --> 44:54.006
Should we fire back to test them?

44:54.208 --> 44:55.084
What for?

44:55.500 --> 44:57.002
Better keep our lives. Run.

44:57.167 --> 44:58.043
Run.

45:02.000 --> 45:04.128
Even if we annihilate Yin Chang,

45:04.542 --> 45:05.714
so what?

45:06.833 --> 45:07.880
He's of no consequence.

45:08.292 --> 45:10.090
The real battle is ahead of us.

45:10.792 --> 45:11.588
Yes.

45:12.417 --> 45:13.464
You want to cut my queue?

45:14.000 --> 45:14.421
Fine.

45:14.792 --> 45:15.463
Come.

45:21.792 --> 45:24.090
Since you revolutionaries
have bestowed such honour on me,

45:24.625 --> 45:26.593
I'll be presumptuous and break the law.

45:38.917 --> 45:40.419
Father.

45:45.917 --> 45:47.009
Good news.

45:47.375 --> 45:49.048
You scared away my fish.

45:51.958 --> 45:53.460
You're coming out of seclusion.

45:58.375 --> 45:59.968
You can't hold your horses, can you?

46:23.250 --> 46:24.672
General, Huafu is here.

46:27.292 --> 46:28.293
Huafu.

46:28.958 --> 46:30.005
Let's show

46:30.333 --> 46:33.382
the revolutionaries and
those in the Forbidden City

46:33.875 --> 46:35.343
our great Beiyang Army

46:36.500 --> 46:37.672
and our great power.

46:37.875 --> 46:38.376
Yes.

46:38.750 --> 46:40.343
Attention, artillery.

46:40.500 --> 46:42.218
Target ahead,

46:42.542 --> 46:44.260
25m to the right,

46:44.500 --> 46:45.717
distance at 500.

46:45.958 --> 46:47.335
Load.

46:47.500 --> 46:48.922
Ready.

46:51.625 --> 46:52.171
Fire.

47:21.375 --> 47:22.217
Alcohol.

