Keqiang.

48:10.500 --> 48:11.877
Where should We go?

48:13.708 --> 48:15.551
Wherever there's heavy gunfire.

48:17.583 --> 48:18.425
Make way.

48:19.125 --> 48:19.796
Make way.

48:25.333 --> 48:26.084
Commander.

48:39.125 --> 48:40.047
Avoid gunfire.

48:40.458 --> 48:41.630
Avoid gunfire.

48:41.792 --> 48:43.169
Hide in the trench with your squad.

48:43.417 --> 48:44.259
Hide in the trench.

